1. On *uživa* u čitanju knjiga. (He *enjoys* reading books.)
2. Oni *uživaju* u svom odmoru. (They *are enjoying* their vacation.)
3. Uživao je u ukusnom obroku. (He *enjoyed* the delicious meal.)
4. On *uživa* u slušanju muzike. (He *enjoys* listening to music.)
5. Svi *uživaju* u lepom vremenu. (Everyone *is enjoying* the nice weather.)
6. Njih dvoje *uživaju* u druženju. (The two of them *are enjoying* their time together.)
7. On *uživa* u sportu koji voli. (He *enjoys* the sport he loves.)
8. Deca *uživaju* u igri u parku. (The children *are enjoying* playing in the park.)
9. Ona *uživa* u šetnji pored reke. (She *enjoys* walking by the river.)
10. Uživajte u svom odmoru! (Enjoy your vacation!)